wiki.text:
The word 'qualitative' refers to descriptions or distinctions based on some
quality or characteristic rather than on some quantity or measured value. It
can be a form of analysis that yields the identity of a compound. It may
also refer to:

*Qualitative property, a property that can be observed but not measured
numerically *Qualitative research, a research paradigm focusing on non-
quantifiable measurements *Qualitative data, data that is not quantified
